    </header>

    <div class="flexbox-wrap main-content">
        <div class="coming_soon card">
            <img class="in-card-img" src="/img/exciting.jpg" alt="Coming Soon Graphic">
            <div class="flexbox-wrap-col card-text">
                <h2>You wont believe what is coming!</h2>
